{"tid":97443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）新年流流部洗衣機壞左，點算","createTime":"2017-01-27T15:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T11:05:58.000Z","uid":31847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4a53b45e8bcf3bbed2d6b4f80d867739e3b6d1","tid":97443,"uid":31847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:58:27.000Z","msg":"部洗衣機係zanussi 日式洗衣機果隻<br />\n岩岩洗洗下出左E5，睇說明書話係排水排唔到，之後將條喉放落地下等佢流啦<br />\n佢出水出得好弱，又有d噠噠聲，唔知咩事<br />\n<br />\n試過拆開去水喉個出水位，冇野塞住，再拆開機背，見到d水積住左係入面條喉到，前面果舊其實咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋舊野熱到有d辣手<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/27/235054_0fc8add6b000cc864d273c4d3578a7bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F27%2F235054_0fc8add6b000cc864d273c4d3578a7bb.jpg&h=a12a8574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重點：大昌行維修既話係唔係一定要7日內寄返張保養佢，個保養先會生效？我已經過左幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋，有冇知佢地年初幾先開工</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac9f3702778510464854ed3d19851d46da83878","tid":97443,"uid":31847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a622ace9dd44a4206383c9cb323e961ee1833e","tid":97443,"uid":31847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" cl